text: Tareq Khouri (; 1 December 1967 in Amman) is a Jordanian businessman and former president of Al-Wehdat SC. He is a deputy to the Parliament of Jordan."MP Khoury apologises over tweets after case against him dropped", The Jordan Times, 22 March 2015 ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Jordanian businesspeople Category:People from Amman
title: Tareq Khouri
